## L.1 Engine Architecture Principle

Modality engines are **AGI-first**: they can run fully headlessly. The UI layer is optional and additive. An engine pipeline:

1. Works headlessly via its standard pipeline interface (`--input JSON`)
2. Optionally exposes a UI through Electron/React injection (if running in desktop mode)
